                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </nav>

        <header id="gtco-header" class="gtco-cover gtco-cover-md" role="banner" style="background-image: url(../../Photos/4.jpg)">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="gtco-container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12 col-md-offset-0 text-left">
                        <div class="row row-mt-15em">
                            <div class="col-md-7 mt-text animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeInUp">
                                <h1>有服章之美谓之华<br>有礼仪之大谓之夏</h1>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="gtco-section">
            <div class="gtco-container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center gtco-heading">
                        <h2>衣裳为谁施</h2>
                        <p>服饰作为一种文化形态，贯穿了中国古代各个时期的历史。从服饰的演变中可以看出历史的变迁、经济的发展和中国文化审美意识的嬗变。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    @foreach (var item in Model.Relic1)
                    {
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                            <a href="~/Photos/@item.Himage" class="fh5co-card-item image-popup">
                                <figure>
                                    <img src="~/Photos/@item.Himage" alt="Image" class="img-responsive">
                                </figure>
                                <div class="fh5co-text">
                                    <h2>@item.name</h2>
                                    <p>@item.describle</p>
                                    @*<p><span class="btn btn-primary">了解更多</span></p>*@
                                    @*<a href="@Url.Action("RelicDetail","Relic",new {Reid=@item.HFId })">了解更多</a>*@
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>

                    }

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>




        <div id="gtco-features" class="gtco-cover gtco-cover-md" role="banner" style="background-image: url(../../Photos/ac01.jpg)">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="gtco-container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center gtco-heading animate-box">
                        <h2>活动</h2>
                        <p>从理论融入到生活，从生活提升为仰，汉服将离开舞台与博物馆，走向每一个人的日常。汉式生活展是以汉服走进生活为主题的一系列活动，每月一期，每期都有不同的主题，主题均与衣食住行相关，我们希望有一天汉服能像时装一样，成为我们生活中必不可少的物件。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    @foreach (var p in Model.Activity1)
                    {
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                            <div class="feature-center animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                                <span class="icon">
                                    <i>@p.ActiId</i>
                                </span>
                                <h3>@p.Title</h3>
                                <p>@p.Content</p>
                                <a href="@Url.Action("ActivityDetail","Activity",new {ActId=@p.ActiId})"></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    }
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>



        <div id="gtco-counter" class="gtco-section">
            <div class="gtco-container">

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center gtco-heading animate-box">
                        <h2>社区</h2>
                        <p>Dignissimos asperiores vitae velit veniam totam fuga molestias accusamus alias autem provident. Odit ab aliquam dolor eius.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">


                    <style>
                        .def_nav_info {
                            width: 1100px;
                            height: 100%;
                            margin: 0px auto;
                        }

                            .def_nav_info a {
                                margin-left: 140px;
